Date: Fri, 1 May 2026 10:42:44 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 25/43] PopUpWindowController: Fix notification popup task
 ownership

Fix task ownership bookkeeping for notification-launched pop-up tasks so later updates target the actual active task rather than the originating notification record.

Change-Id: I7709d7f84225e6ffb81491cb26337f093877e91a
---
 .../server/wm/PopUpWindowController.java      | 48 +++++++++++--------
 .../server/wm/TaskWindowSurfaceInfo.java      | 24 +++++++---
 .../server/wm/TopActivityRecorder.java        |  7 +--
 3 files changed, 48 insertions(+), 31 deletions(-)

